divs: Sighting DetailsSaw the light at first wondered if it was a helicopter, clearly saw it wasn't, stopped vehicle to watch it, it started turning to red and made a square formation then disappeared. Was positive it was not something of ours as we have an airport as well as an air force base nearby and often watch their crafts. This was nothing I have seen before.
Summary: Ball of light, moving upward, then in a square pattern, then turned red and dissappeared
trends: There have been 19 other sightings in Oxnard
